## Rooms for improvement for a chatbot:

1. Utilizing knowledge graph
2. Optimizing the code to perform parallel and sequntial tasks in the right way
3. Handling large databases and users (Search base on the last few months and not the whole database)
4. Control the context length and the input size (70%)
5. Controlling the system role
6. Improve the summary model (both performance and strategy)
7. Optimize the system roles and instructions
8. Add more tools


1 database for the chat session
1 shared database for all the chat sessions (vector database)
1 knowledge graph database for better user info




